<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-17T04:36:14-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-17T04:36:14-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T04:36:14-05:00</updated><title> Bellroy 的 iPhone 15 Pro 手机壳现在有一个合适的操作按钮</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示操作和音量按钮的外壳侧面特写。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4fxWt7sfz0xoEkcq3Vo1de_Lo3g=/0x0:3200x2133/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72874846/bellroy_pcxi_terracotta_print_04.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;用传统按钮代替切口。&lt;/em>; |图片来源：Bellroy&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;080fcy&quot;>;苹果决定在 iPhone 15 Pro 系列上用操作按钮取代静音开关，导致一些手机壳制造商措手不及，两个月后，Bellroy 推出了发布了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fbellroy.com%2Fproducts%2Fphone-case%3Fcolor%3Dblack%26material%3Dleather %26size%3Di15promax%23slide-0&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2F23965171%2Fbellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button -cutout&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;已更新&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A% 2F%2Fbellroy.com%2Fproducts%2Fphone-case-3-card%3Fcolor%3Deverglade%26material%3Dleather%26size%3Di15promax%23slide-0&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge。 com%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2F23965171%2Fbellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;范围&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fbellroy.com%2Fproducts%2Fmod-phone-case-wallet%3Fcolor%3Dterracotta%26material%3Dleather%26size% 3Di15promax%23slide-0&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2F23965171%2Fbellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout&quot; rel =“赞助的nofollow noopener”target =“_blank”>;案例&lt;/a>;。与第一次运行时的操作按钮上有一个切口，可能会使其难以伸手按下，新设计有一个更标准的集成按钮。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;pVlaLz&quot;>;“新设计外壳上还包括另一个按钮，可提供与实际设备相同的功能和体验。这更加自然和无缝，”Bellroy 的产品开发主管 Arya Ghavifekr 说道。贝尔罗伊表示，任何购买了第一批带有切口的箱子的人都可以将其换成新型号。它继续销售旧手机壳...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965171/bellroy-iphone-15-pro-case -action-button-cutout&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965171/bellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965171/bellroy-iphone-15-pro-case-action-button-cutout</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-16T21:10:41-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-16T21:10:41-05:00</updated><title> Steam Deck 的大幅稳定更新为 Dock 带来了全新功能</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Steam Deck Dock&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/y1ei103hfuTCJzVcALdxNbrSGI0=/391x0:2500x1406/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/72874172/steamdeckdockback.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Valve&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;V7KU2a&quot;>;Valve 的新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /23951655/steam-deck-oled-review&quot;>;Steam Deck OLED&lt;/a>; 今天刚刚上市，但原始 LCD 型号也有好东西 - 该公司是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://store .steampowered.com/news/app/1675200/view/5484882897552407488&quot;>;现在推出 SteamOS 3.5.5 的稳定版本&lt;/a>;，其中包含大量修复、更改和升级。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;ZbhI6k&quot;>;一些最大的是我们已经见过的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/15/23875824/valve-steam-deck-steamos-3-5 -preview-vrr-hdr-starfield&quot;>;9 月测试版&lt;/a>;，例如对 VRR 和 HDR 外部显示器的支持、调整屏幕颜色并使用新固件对处理器进行降压的能力，以及使用&lt;em>;Starfield&lt;/em>; 的性能大幅提升（